1	## 1. Executive Summary\nThis document evaluates the adoption of **Biome** as a replacement for the traditional ESLint and Prettier stack for upcoming Next.js projects at VATECH Networks. Biome is a Rust-based, high-performance toolchain that unifies linting, formatting, and import sorting. By leveraging a multi-threaded architecture, Biome offers significant improvements in CI/CD pipeline efficiency and developer experience (DX).	[0.0031969012,0.044366844,-0.01804863,-0.0071835206,-0.0086976485,0.0012710231,-0.04294937,0.005566357,0.036892194,-0.055103548,-0.03699861,0.008101515,0.038448073,-0.013649448,-0.021885602,0.011058918,0.03984268,0.0014359375,-0.021584354,0.012659498,0.013684739,-0.0039000206,0.032959003,0.010839375,0.0034046175,0.015888784,-0.023856102,0.0025991448,-0.040813133,0.17373127,-0.026057694,-0.024701979,-0.0037307593,-0.018595522,0.006276358,-0.034174945,-0.013546985,0.0039938786,-0.017231971,-0.020917654,-0.020546243,0.01055386,-0.0030438947,7.11313e-05,0.0042393124,-0.0017639452,0.0073130783,0.023051312,-0.0053727147,-0.03072,0.004528047,0.0019343098,0.031724423,-0.016498784,-0.0133480765,-0.008767212,0.039792027,-0.025086854,0.008339639,0.014354431,0.013960986,0.009703845,0.08154787,0.028231379,0.0022254663,0.005107482,0.061165918,-0.036561243,-0.007946392,0.0024489074,0.01907013,0.020687144,-0.028255882,-0.0067433887,0.02257023,0.012295143,-0.035634026,0.018611852,-0.006409766,-0.0019152971,0.01059116,-0.033689633,-0.025415368,-0.02265509,0.004453239,0.013438928,-0.007739122,0.009690551,0.0024486652,-0.032826234,0.044300772,0.0013053851,0.015047305,0.018534698,-0.024065958,0.017286818,-0.002543666,-0.018868482,-0.007705954,0.011462144,-0.022399811,-0.00036830557,-0.00935798,0.021593586,0.006576311,0.023056984,-0.020735484,-0.00797161,-0.005163973,-0.009205747,-0.04829761,-0.2425769,0.014156259,0.009964917,0.022760876,-0.05147219,-0.031343035,0.007895303,0.019444937,0.030698102,0.017872931,0.023097103,-0.031989258,-0.021826558,-0.003234162