7	### 5.1 Ecosystem and Plugins\n*   **Limited Plugin Support:** Biome does not support the massive ESLint plugin ecosystem (1,000+ plugins). It currently provides ~420 built-in rules.\n*   **Niche Rule Gaps:** Certain security-specific or framework-specific rules (e.g., `eslint-config-next` image optimization) are not yet natively supported.\n*   **Custom Rules:** While Biome v2.0 introduced plugin support via **GritQL**, the learning curve is steeper than writing JavaScript-based ESLint rules, and the supporting community remains small.	[0.0054792743,0.028648736,0.001014941,-0.018987294,0.021153476,-0.027811872,-0.016951716,-0.03122383,0.0025586495,-0.06669822,-0.0075470293,0.027934311,0.0076164743,-0.009784389,-0.020757467,0.028590877,0.014277147,0.009320662,-0.014422574,0.014684085,0.0081927795,0.0044478183,0.002617516,0.05218325,0.014158343,0.019495059,0.0076190257,0.022389298,-0.029121846,0.17487733,-0.035247684,-0.012358341,0.020118332,-0.005743646,-0.008430271,-0.04904439,-0.022661194,-0.004597866,-0.0030428094,0.00014243528,-0.018023355,0.016933082,0.0016957908,-0.009668803,0.008867733,-0.014471116,0.0073569384,0.01142116,-0.029005405,0.0049612657,-0.014712123,0.029078124,0.01672563,-0.010876951,0.029881967,0.0068522305,0.024580717,0.003210901,0.020937815,0.03399786,-0.011603458,0.026657403,0.032638196,0.0073014735,-0.008388532,0.013036435,0.041879356,-0.01854439,0.0238775,0.008388836,0.0034942972,0.025582736,-0.021505965,-0.0151119325,-0.012595189,0.006354692,-0.038548294,0.006119986,0.001264566,0.03424181,0.027592726,-0.015691236,-0.04014074,0.019563198,0.008635836,0.033237137,0.0075657936,0.018110473,0.009278828,-0.026131405,0.02074546,0.0055570095,0.03757086,-0.0074727302,-0.037470527,0.0182215,-0.02090362,-0.038747262,-0.035711855,-0.013186661,-0.02342136,0.010054574,0.0021633622,0.0032417914,0.018894661,0.002443868,-0.030603413,0.013398728,0.00090039155,-0.026961684,-0.031486515,-0.24213053,-0.013522713,-0.043098927,0.0038465292,-0.035588037,0.0080400